exxonmobils businesses, new and ongoing measures aretaken to prevent and
minimize the impact of our operations on air,water and ground. these
include a significant investment in refining infrastructure and technology to
manufacture clean fuels as well asprojects to monitor and reduce nitrogen
oxide, sulfur oxide and greenhouse gas emissions and expenditures for asset
